/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≡ [SMOD ]» -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `polynomial -/

theorem eval {R : Type _} [CommRing R] {I : Ideal R} {x y : R} (h : «expr ≡ [SMOD ]» x y I) (f : polynomial R) :
    «expr ≡ [SMOD ]» (f.eval x) (f.eval y) I := by
  rw [SModEq.def] at h⊢
  show Ideal.Quotient.mk I (f.eval x) = Ideal.Quotient.mk I (f.eval y)
  change Ideal.Quotient.mk I x = Ideal.Quotient.mk I y at h
  rw [← Polynomial.eval₂_at_apply, ← Polynomial.eval₂_at_apply, h]
#align eval eval

comap:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →ₗ[ ] » -/

theorem comap {f : «expr →ₗ[ ] » M R N} (hxy : «expr ≡ [SMOD ]» (f x) (f y) V) : «expr ≡ [SMOD ]» x y (V.comap f) :=
  (Submodule.Quotient.eq _).2 <| show f (x - y) ∈ V from (f.map_sub x y).symm ▸ (Submodule.Quotient.eq _).1 hxy
